HANSEN v. VOGELSANG. (Supreme Court, Appellate Division, Second Department. July 29, 1910.) Appeal from Nassau County Court Action by Andrew Hansen against Lena Vogelsang. Prom a certain order, defendant appeals. Reversed, and new trial ordered.

Argued before HIRSCHBERG, P. J., and WOODWARD, JENKS, RICH, and CARR, JJ.

*439PER 'CURIAM:

Order of the County Court of Nassau county reversed, and new trial ordered; costs to abide the event. See opinion by RICH, J., 124 N. Y. Supp. 437.

HIRSCHBERG, P. J., concurs in result.
